description: Rita's Italian Ice is a delicious blend of our proprietary mix and fresh fruit, blended flavor through and through to the bottom of every cup. Our flavors include Cookies n Cream, Coconut, Cotton Candy, Cherry, Mango, Watermelon and much, much  more! Our frozen custard is the smoothest, creamiest delight in a cup or on a cone.  Flavors are Vanilla and Chocolate.  We also have the unique blend of Ice and Custard layered in the cup, or blended as a drink, and even blended with toppings.
name: Rita's Italian Ice and Frozen Custard                        Closed!
